1. *Loše* mu je prolazilo poslednje ispite. (He was doing badly on his last tests.) 
2. Šta je bilo *loše* u njegovom ponašanju? (What was wrong with his behavior?) 
3. Njegovo zdravlje se *loše* poboljšalo. (His health has not improved much.) 
4. Mislim da je *loše* odlučio da ode. (I think it was a bad decision for him to leave.) 
5. *Loše* vreme na putu je usporilo njegovu vožnju. (The bad weather on the way slowed down his driving.)